{
  "stem": "311.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was amazed with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he picked it up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "About two, three days later, he did it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, I give him the next blueprint.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He understood.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was so smart, that he could understand the print.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It-- it-- fast, he could pick it up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That man, you know, to me, he was an old man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, I'm older than him now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, I feel old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, come on, this-- that's-- that's what it is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People, whatever it is, they still-- whoever was in the camp, or you was a kapo, or you was a policeman, he did have respect.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The minister of justice, OK?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, he was with--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The factory had to be set up, complete.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Forget about pots and pans, what they were doing in a-- in-- in Enmalia, over there, in-- in Plazow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to do-- we had to do the outer shell from a anti-aircraft bullet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So here comes a-- a new story, a new trade.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew completely nothing, with people like me, my father, Gunter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ginter knew how to set up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a master electrician.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He set up the machines.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have to hook them up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had to give power to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father knew how to bury the machines to bring them up, you know how much foundation they're going to need.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, a 300-ton press needs like 8-foot square, all around, you know, certain stone and cement and so much pig iron and all whatever it is to set up the presses.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they start setting up all the presses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, and-- and what do you do with 700 people?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I think, all right, four lathes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of them I work is number three, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
